headline: Texas Instruments board declares third quarter 2025 quarterly dividend
summary: The board of directors of Texas Instruments Incorporated (Nasdaq: TXN) today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.36 per share of common stock, payable August 12, 2025, to stockholders of record on July 31, 2025.
